thread.title: Helen Will
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Helen Will

author: Helen Will
title: Helen Will
text:
Just think you need to stress to ALL clients that secure packing is essential. Everything must be tied down very very securely. My items weren't, and when I asked for access a few things were scratched as they had bounce around when Box lifted down. I had no idea the Box would be elevated and fork lifts moving it. As someone else packed Box for me I can't recall whether there was provision inside to tie straps onto something secure.
Helen
